<body>
<div class="deck">
  <div class="slide active" data-slide="1">
    <div class="gradient-mesh">
      <div class="blob" style="width:460px;height:460px;top:-80px;right:-80px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.14"></div>
      <div class="blob" style="width:300px;height:300px;left:-60px;bottom:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.11"></div>
      <div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;left:18%;top:42%;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.10"></div>
    </div>
    <canvas class="particle-canvas" style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1" width="300" height="150"></canvas>
    <div class="content text-center">
      <div class="reveal text-[110px] mb-4" style="transition: opacity 0.35s, transform 0.35s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px);">⚠️</div>
      <h1 class="reveal font-display text-[clamp(2.4rem,5.6vw,4.8rem)] font-bold bg-linear-to-r from-accent-1 via-accent-2 to-accent-3 bg-clip-text text-transparent" style="transition: opacity 0.35s 0.08s, transform 0.35s 0.08s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px);">Problems Faced Before This Project</h1>
      <p class="reveal mt-4 text-[1.1rem] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-text-muted" style="transition: opacity 0.35s 0.16s, transform 0.35s 0.16s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px);">Smart Green Hydrogen Process System</p>
      <p class="reveal mt-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg text-text-secondary" style="transition: opacity 0.35s 0.24s, transform 0.35s 0.24s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px);">A presentation on the major production, storage, transport, data, and monitoring limitations that existed before building an integrated digital hydrogen management platform.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="2"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:320px;height:320px;right:-70px;top:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:260px;height:260px;left:-50px;bottom:-50px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.07"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Introduction</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Why management was difficult</h2><div class="twofive"><div class="reveal glass p-7"><ul class="bullets text-lg text-text-secondary"><li>Green hydrogen systems combine renewable power, electrolysis, storage tanks, transport logistics, and safety controls.</li><li>Without a digital platform, each stage works in isolation and decisions depend on delayed manual observations.</li><li>Operators cannot continuously match renewable power input with hydrogen production demand and storage capacity.</li><li>Safety risks increase because hydrogen is colorless, odorless, highly flammable, and needs continuous monitoring.</li></ul></div><div class="reveal glass p-7"><div class="ascii">Solar/Wind  ---&gt;  Electrolyzer  ---&gt;  Storage  ---&gt;  Transport
   |               |                 |            |
 Manual check   Manual log       Tank note    Phone update
   |               |                 |            |
 Delayed data -&gt; Inaccurate plans -&gt; Low visibility -&gt; Slow action</div><p class="mt-4 small text-text-secondary">This fragmented workflow caused poor coordination, slow reporting, and inefficient system control.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="3"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:340px;height:340px;top:-80px;right:-80px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-40px;left:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Production</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Problems in hydrogen production</h2><div class="cardgrid"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Lack of real-time energy monitoring</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Solar and wind output changes every hour. Without live power data, the system cannot decide the best electrolyzer operating point.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Low energy-use efficiency</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Renewable electricity may be underused, wasted, or replaced by unsuitable grid power because load balancing is manual.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Manual hydrogen estimation</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Production values are often estimated using rough calculations, causing mismatch between expected and actual hydrogen output.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Weather-driven inconsistency</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Cloud cover, wind variation, and seasonal changes interrupt production planning and make continuous output difficult.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="4"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:300px;height:300px;right:-60px;top:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.09"></div><div class="blob" style="width:240px;height:240px;left:-40px;bottom:-50px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Production</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Impact of manual calculations</h2><div class="three"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🧮</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Arithmetic mistakes</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Errors in current, voltage, efficiency, and time calculations affect hydrogen yield values.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🔁</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Unit conversion errors</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Confusion between kWh, kg, liters, and pressure units creates inaccurate production records.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">📉</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Poor planning</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Incorrect estimates lead to wrong tank allocation, delayed dispatch, and unreliable demand support.</p></div></div><div class="reveal glass p-7 mt-6"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">Example: If solar output falls suddenly but the production team continues with the previous schedule, the electrolyzer may run inefficiently, consume non-optimal power, and produce less hydrogen than expected.</p></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="5"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:330px;height:330px;top:-80px;right:-80px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:250px;height:250px;bottom:-50px;left:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.07"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Storage</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Problems in hydrogen storage</h2><div class="cardgrid"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">No live tank-level monitoring</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Operators do not know exact pressure, quantity, or fill level at the required time.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Overfilling and underutilization</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Without automated checks, some tanks may be overfilled while other capacity remains unused.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Poor tracking of available hydrogen</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Inventory visibility becomes weak when production records and tank records are separated.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Safety and alert gaps</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Pressure rise, leakage risk, and abnormal conditions may go unnoticed because alerting is manual.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="6"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:320px;height:320px;right:-70px;top:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;left:-20px;bottom:-40px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Storage safety</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Why poor monitoring is risky</h2><div class="twofive"><div class="reveal glass p-7"><ul class="bullets text-lg text-text-secondary"><li>Hydrogen is highly flammable and needs rapid leak detection.</li><li>Poor pressure and temperature supervision may lead to unsafe storage conditions.</li><li>Manual inspection cannot provide round-the-clock safety coverage.</li><li>Lack of alarms delays emergency response and increases operational risk.</li></ul></div><div class="reveal glass p-7"><div class="ascii">Tank Status Check
-------------
Level        : Unknown
Pressure     : Delayed reading
Leak status  : Not continuously checked
Alarm        : Not automated
Decision     : Based on old data</div><p class="mt-4 small text-text-secondary">Modern hydrogen systems require continuous sensing, rapid leak detection, and timely notification for safer operation.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="7"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:330px;height:330px;top:-80px;right:-80px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:250px;height:250px;bottom:-60px;left:-40px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.07"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Transportation</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Problems in hydrogen transportation</h2><div class="three"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🚚</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Manual delivery tracking</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Status updates are shared through phone calls, paper slips, or separate spreadsheets.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">⏳</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Frequent delays</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Lack of coordinated scheduling causes dispatch delay, waiting time, and confusion at destination points.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🗺️</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">No route optimization</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Routes are not optimized using traffic, distance, urgency, or vehicle load conditions.</p></div></div><div class="reveal glass p-7 mt-6"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">Inventory in transport is also difficult to track, so the sending site, vehicle operator, and receiving site may all hold different records for the same hydrogen batch.</p></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="8"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:300px;height:300px;right:-70px;top:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:240px;height:240px;left:-30px;bottom:-40px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Data</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Data management problems</h2><div class="cardgrid"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Paper-based records</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Production values, tank logs, and delivery notes are often maintained manually and are hard to search.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Data duplication</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Different departments may record the same information separately, creating mismatch and repetition.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Missing or inaccurate records</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Late updates and human entry mistakes reduce trust in the information used for planning.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">No centralized database</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Historical data, status logs, and analytics are difficult to access without a single integrated system.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="9"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:320px;height:320px;top:-70px;right:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:230px;height:230px;left:-20px;bottom:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Monitoring</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Reporting and decision-making issues</h2><div class="twofive"><div class="reveal glass p-7"><ul class="bullets text-lg text-text-secondary"><li>No live dashboard for production, storage, and transport status.</li><li>Report preparation takes time because data must be collected from many sources.</li><li>Trend analysis is weak due to inconsistent historical data.</li><li>Critical notifications are not automatically sent to operators or administrators.</li><li>Management decisions become reactive instead of data-driven.</li></ul></div><div class="reveal glass p-7"><div class="ascii">Without Dashboard:
Production  -&gt; separate log
Storage     -&gt; separate sheet
Transport   -&gt; phone update
Reports      -&gt; manual compilation
Decision     -&gt; delayed and incomplete</div><p class="mt-4 small text-text-secondary">A disconnected monitoring process reduces situational awareness and slows corrective action.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="10"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:330px;height:330px;right:-70px;top:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.09"></div><div class="blob" style="width:240px;height:240px;left:-30px;bottom:-40px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.07"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Environment</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Environmental problems before the project</h2><div class="three"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🏭</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Fossil fuel dependence</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Poor renewable coordination may force the system to rely on conventional power sources.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🌫️</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Higher carbon emissions</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Hydrogen loses its environmental value if production is not aligned with clean electricity use.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">⚡</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Renewable energy wastage</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Unused surplus solar or wind energy may be curtailed instead of converted into useful hydrogen.</p></div></div><div class="reveal glass p-7 mt-6"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">Inefficient scheduling also increases energy wastage and makes sustainability goals harder to achieve in practice.</p></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="11"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:320px;height:320px;right:-70px;top:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:230px;height:230px;left:-20px;bottom:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.07"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Operations</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Operational challenges</h2><div class="cardgrid"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">High manpower demand</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">More staff time is needed for log entry, validation, tank observation, transport coordination, and report preparation.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Human recording errors</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Manual entries easily introduce wrong timestamps, duplicate records, and omitted values.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Slow emergency response</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Without automatic alarms and centralized information, abnormal conditions are handled slowly.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Poor department coordination</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Production, storage, and transport teams often work using separate records and separate communication channels.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="12"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:320px;height:320px;top:-70px;right:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;left:-20px;bottom:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Technology</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">Technical challenges</h2><div class="three"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🔗</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">No system integration</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Renewable generation, electrolysis, storage, and transport remain disconnected.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">📊</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">No smart analytics</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">The system cannot detect patterns, optimize usage, or generate predictive insights.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">📈</div><h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Difficult to scale</h3><p class="tiny text-text-secondary">Expanding the plant, tanks, or fleet becomes harder when digital infrastructure is weak.</p></div></div><div class="reveal glass p-7 mt-6"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">The absence of predictive monitoring means that many failures are recognized only after they affect production or safety.</p></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="13"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:340px;height:340px;top:-70px;right:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:240px;height:240px;left:-20px;bottom:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><canvas class="particle-canvas-ambient" style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1" width="300" height="150"></canvas><div class="content"><p class="reveal section-tag">Combined impact</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-5xl mb-6">How the problems affected the system</h2><div class="cardgrid"><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Lower efficiency</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Energy, time, and manpower were used inefficiently because the system could not self-coordinate.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Lower safety</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Poor visibility over tank conditions and transport status increased the possibility of unsafe operation.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Lower reliability</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Irregular production and weak records made supply planning and delivery commitments difficult.</p></div><div class="reveal glass p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Lower sustainability</h3><p class="small text-text-secondary">Renewable resources were not fully utilized, reducing the environmental value of the hydrogen workflow.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="14"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:460px;height:460px;top:-90px;right:-80px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.14"></div><div class="blob" style="width:300px;height:300px;left:-60px;bottom:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.12"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;left:18%;top:40%;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.10"></div></div><canvas class="particle-canvas" style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1" width="300" height="150"></canvas><div class="content text-center"><p class="reveal section-tag">Summary</p><h2 class="reveal font-display text-[clamp(2.2rem,5vw,4.4rem)] mb-6">Need for a smart process system</h2><div class="reveal glass p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">These problems clearly show that manual and disconnected methods are not suitable for modern green hydrogen production, storage, and transportation. A smart process system is needed to provide real-time monitoring, centralized data, automated alerts, better planning, improved safety, and efficient use of renewable energy across the full hydrogen workflow.</p></div><p class="reveal mt-8 text-text-muted tracking-[0.28em] uppercase">Digital monitoring • safer storage • smarter transport • better sustainability</p></div></div>
</div>

